* Iran recognized Azerbaijan on January 4, 1992, upgraded its consulate in [[Baku]] to establish full diplomatic relations.&lt;ref name=&quot;nichol150&quot;&gt;James P. Nichol. ''Diplomacy in the Former Soviet Republics'', Praeger/Greenwood, 1995, ISBN 0275951928, p. 150&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web|last= |first= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Country Studies/Azerbaijan/The Foreign Policy Establishment |work= |publisher=http://countrystudies.us|date= |url=http://countrystudies.us/azerbaijan/36.htm |doi= |accessdate=January 18, 2008}}&lt;/ref&gt;
