===No relations===
[[Image:Azerbaijan relations.png|right|350px|Diplomatic relations of Azerbaijan]]
Azerbaijan maintains diplomatic relations with 166 states (including [[State of Palestine|Palestine]] and the [[Vatican City]]) and the [[European Union]]. Azerbaijan has not yet established diplomatic with:&lt;ref&gt;[http://mfa.gov.az/eng/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=223&amp;Itemid=1 Azerbaijan MFA - diplomatic relations]&lt;/ref&gt;
