* Armenia is represented in Cyprus through its embassy in [[Athens]] (Greece).
* Cyprus is represented in Armenia through its embassy in Moscow, (Russia) and through an honorary consulate in [[Yerevan]].  * There are around 2,750 people of [[Armenian diaspora|Armenian descent]] living in Cyprus.&lt;ref&gt;[http://www.hayem.org/ Hayem.org website for Armenian Cypriots, accessed 10 Feb, 2011]&lt;/ref&gt;
