*[[1995]] &amp;ndash; [[Jan Křesadlo]], Czech writer (b. 1926)
*  1995   &amp;ndash; [[Alison Hargreaves]], British mountaineer (b. 1963)
*  1995   &amp;ndash; [[Mickey Mantle]], American baseball player (b. 1931)
*  1995   &amp;ndash; [[Rob Slater]], American mountaineer (b. 1960)
*[[1996]] &amp;ndash; [[António de Spínola]], Portuguese general and politician (b. 1910)
*  1996   &amp;ndash; [[David Tudor]], American pianist and composer (b. 1926)
*[[1998]] &amp;ndash; [[Nino Ferrer]], Italian-born French singer and composer (b. 1934)
*  1998   &amp;ndash; [[Julien Green]], American novelist (b. 1900)
*  1998   &amp;ndash; [[Waneta Hoyt]], American serial killer (b. 1946)
*[[1999]] &amp;ndash; [[Jaime Garzón]], Colombian journalist and comedian (b. 1960)
*[[2000]] &amp;ndash; [[Nazia Hassan]], Pakistani pop singer (b. 1965)
*[[2001]] &amp;ndash; [[Otto Stuppacher]], Austrian race car driver (b. 1947)
*[[2003]] &amp;ndash; [[Ed Townsend]], American songwriter and producer (b. 1929)
*[[2004]] &amp;ndash; [[Julia Child]], American chef and television personality (b. 1912)
*[[2005]] &amp;ndash; [[David Lange]], 32&lt;sup&gt;nd&lt;/sup&gt; [[Prime Minister of New Zealand]] (b. 1942)
*[[2006]] &amp;ndash; [[Tony Jay]], English actor (b. 1933)
*  2006   &amp;ndash; [[Jon Nödtveidt]], Swedish vocalist (b. 1975)
*  2006   &amp;ndash; [[Payao Poontarat]], Thai boxer (b. 1957)
*[[2007]] &amp;ndash; [[Brian Adams (wrestler)|Brian Adams]], American professional wrestler (b. 1964)
*  2007   &amp;ndash; [[Brooke Astor]], American philanthropist (b. 1902)
*  2007   &amp;ndash; [[Yone Minagawa]], Japanese supercentenarian (b. 1893)
