| main_interests   = [[Medicine]], [[philosophy]], [[Islamic theology]] ([[kalam]]), [[physics]], [[Persian poetry|poetry]], [[science]], [[paleontology]]
| notable_ideas    = Father of modern [[medicine]]; [[Avicennian logic]]; concepts of [[inertia]] and [[momentum]]; forerunner of [[psychoanalysis]]; important contributor to [[geology]]; pioneer of [[aromatherapy]] and [[neuropsychiatry]]
| major_works      = ''[[The Book of Healing]]'', ''[[The Canon of Medicine]]''
